# Project Overview

The **Synergy** program has two interconnected Power Apps sharing one Dataverse environment.

## Applications

1. **Project Management** (model-driven) — Partners, Projects, Contracts, Resources.
   Used by PMs, BDUs, Resource Managers. Feeds data INTO the Invoice app.
2. **Invoice Canvas** (Canvas) — create, manage, and track invoices.
   Reads partner/project/contract data from the PM app. Stores invoices in
   `dia_invoicedetails` / EntitySetName `dia_invoicedetailses`.
   **This is the primary app under automation.**

